					</marginalia_text>
					<emphasis method="chalk" type="straight"/>
				</position>
				<position place="tail" book_orientation="270">
					<marginalia_text>
						concessio.
					</marginalia_text>
				</position>
			</language>
			<translation>
				An example for all in terms of Rhetoric, irony, paradox, hyperbole, ellipsis, aporia, permissio, concessio.
			</translation>
		</marginalia>
		
